WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 38=

01:48.300 --> 01:52.180
(Suburbs of Nanjing)

01:57.500 --> 01:58.340
Your Majesty,

01:59.220 --> 02:00.470
please punish me.

02:01.830 --> 02:02.670
During the riot,

02:04.190 --> 02:05.110
the late emperor was trapped.

02:05.670 --> 02:07.190
I failed to return in time.

02:08.580 --> 02:09.900
So, the two of you

02:10.420 --> 02:11.270
fell into danger

02:11.670 --> 02:12.510
without any help.

02:13.020 --> 02:13.860
I...

02:14.350 --> 02:15.190
I am guilty.

02:15.830 --> 02:16.670
I've found out.

02:17.140 --> 02:18.180
This isn't your fault.

02:19.020 --> 02:19.860
Duan,

02:20.510 --> 02:21.350
you're not guilty.

02:26.510 --> 02:28.990
Xianye died for our nation.

02:29.550 --> 02:31.510
How could I leave him in the wilderness?

02:32.700 --> 02:33.540
But sadly,

02:34.110 --> 02:35.860
all I can do is set up this tomb.

02:48.420 --> 02:49.830
I once travelled from Nandu

02:49.830 --> 02:50.790
to different cities.

02:51.670 --> 02:53.180
But I've never been to the border.

02:53.670 --> 02:54.510
Yet I know very well,

02:55.230 --> 02:56.180
this world is very big,

02:57.460 --> 02:58.300
beyond the Palace

02:58.900 --> 02:59.830
and beyond the Capital.

03:00.510 --> 03:01.350
The world

03:01.740 --> 03:03.460
doesn't belong to the emperor,

03:04.300 --> 03:05.630
but to the people all over it.

03:06.420 --> 03:07.260
We are

03:07.860 --> 03:09.580
gradually recovering the 17 Prefectures.

03:10.430 --> 03:11.870
As a member of this nation,

03:13.140 --> 03:14.390
I sincerely thank you.

03:19.620 --> 03:21.070
Fang Ji and I had a promise.

03:23.300 --> 03:24.620
I would retake the 17 Prefectures.

03:25.670 --> 03:27.070
He would be a virtuous minister

03:28.460 --> 03:29.350
to uphold this nation.

03:30.790 --> 03:31.630
But so far,

03:32.860 --> 03:34.300
I haven't fulfilled this promise.

03:37.180 --> 03:38.140
Entrust me

03:38.990 --> 03:39.830
with his last wish.

03:41.350 --> 03:42.830
I'll govern the nation well.

03:44.790 --> 03:45.950
I won't fail

03:46.550 --> 03:47.510
the promise

03:47.510 --> 03:48.670
the three of us made.

03:49.580 --> 03:50.420
My...

03:52.860 --> 03:54.270
My time is running out.

03:55.700 --> 03:56.540
I'm going to die.

03:57.580 --> 03:58.700
Xianye is dead.

03:59.070 --> 04:00.230
You must look after yourself.

04:01.550 --> 04:02.460
I hereby take an oath

04:02.460 --> 04:03.900
upon Xianye's soul.

04:07.860 --> 04:08.700
I'll devote my life

04:11.420 --> 04:13.350
to recovering the 17 Prefectures.

04:16.550 --> 04:17.500
My vow never changes.

04:21.230 --> 04:22.070
Shunxi,

04:22.420 --> 04:23.670
I trust no one but you

04:24.790 --> 04:25.630
on border issues.

04:34.470 --> 04:35.310
You and Fang Ji

04:36.350 --> 04:37.190
can talk in private.

05:01.590 --> 05:02.740
You always said I was insane.

05:05.110 --> 05:06.350
But when you went insane,

05:08.500 --> 05:09.790
you were even more fierce.

05:12.470 --> 05:13.700
People always say

05:16.180 --> 05:17.670
the Top Scholar is self-disciplined.

05:20.260 --> 05:21.350
You were just pretending.

05:23.500 --> 05:24.340
Don't worry.

05:25.620 --> 05:27.110
His Majesty will be a good emperor.

05:28.500 --> 05:30.030
He will bring our nation

05:31.030 --> 05:32.790
into a prosperous age
we've been expecting.

05:34.820 --> 05:35.660
Whether he's a friend

05:36.470 --> 05:37.350
or he's the Emperor,

05:38.670 --> 05:40.260
I believe this will never change.

05:42.670 --> 05:43.940
You used to worry too much.

05:45.550 --> 05:47.110
Now you've died before me.

05:48.910 --> 05:49.860
You can stop worrying

05:52.620 --> 05:53.740
and take some good rest.

05:57.620 --> 05:58.460
And I...

06:05.760 --> 06:06.620
I want to stay

06:06.620 --> 06:07.940
with her for as long as I can.

06:18.460 --> 06:20.380
(Duan Mansion)

06:44.150 --> 06:44.990
I'm here

06:46.150 --> 06:47.260
to bid farewell, Father.

06:48.860 --> 06:49.700
I'm a bad son.

06:50.350 --> 06:51.620
I can't serve you or Mother.

06:52.180 --> 06:53.500
Please take care of yourselves.

06:59.590 --> 07:00.430
Stop right there!

07:08.590 --> 07:09.430
Father,

07:14.170 --> 07:15.570
for our family's glory,

07:17.860 --> 07:19.410
you sacrificed most of your life.

07:22.710 --> 07:24.230
You and Mother both suffered.

07:27.820 --> 07:28.790
I have someone I love

07:32.300 --> 07:33.420
and something I want to do.

07:40.670 --> 07:42.110
I will live for myself.

07:45.420 --> 07:46.260
Duan Xu!

07:46.260 --> 07:47.990
Stop!

07:48.860 --> 07:49.700
Come back!

07:49.860 --> 07:50.940
Come back here!

07:54.940 --> 07:55.780
He...

07:56.620 --> 07:57.460
Come back!

08:01.790 --> 08:02.630
Duan Xu.

08:04.030 --> 08:04.870
Duan Xu.

08:06.670 --> 08:07.510
Come back!

08:10.420 --> 08:11.260
Come back.

08:14.260 --> 08:15.100
Come back here.

08:22.860 --> 08:23.740
When I was little,

08:26.110 --> 08:27.820
I fell into a pit in the backyard.

08:29.820 --> 08:30.790
It was very dark.

08:31.670 --> 08:32.510
And the pit was deep.

08:33.830 --> 08:34.670
I was really scared

08:35.590 --> 08:36.430
and cried for help.

08:39.230 --> 08:40.260
Then I saw my father

08:43.070 --> 08:44.380
standing there and looking at me.

08:47.140 --> 08:48.260
He said he wouldn't help me

08:49.950 --> 08:51.260
or let anyone else help me.

08:52.900 --> 08:53.950
He asked me to climb out.

08:54.900 --> 08:55.740
If I had failed,

08:56.590 --> 08:57.780
I would have died there.

09:01.500 --> 09:02.620
I cried and begged him.

09:05.860 --> 09:06.740
But he still left.

09:10.140 --> 09:11.190
I tried many times

09:14.350 --> 09:15.740
and fell over and over.

09:18.540 --> 09:19.380
In the end,

09:20.650 --> 09:21.500
I did climb out

09:21.500 --> 09:22.340
all by myself.

09:25.260 --> 09:26.100
I was thinking.

09:27.430 --> 09:28.430
So, I could save myself

09:30.500 --> 09:32.030
without begging for help.

09:37.950 --> 09:38.790
Oh, I see.

09:39.540 --> 09:40.740
So when you were abducted,

09:40.740 --> 09:42.260
you didn't blame your father.

09:46.020 --> 09:47.220
It's not quite like that.

09:49.000 --> 09:50.410
After I came back from the Chong,

09:52.070 --> 09:53.070
I heard that day,

09:54.350 --> 09:55.540
my father stood near the pit

09:55.540 --> 09:56.380
and guarded the hole.

09:58.570 --> 09:59.440
He stood in the sun

09:59.460 --> 10:00.530
for several hours.

10:02.540 --> 10:03.540
He didn't leave

10:03.540 --> 10:04.380
until I climbed out.

10:07.620 --> 10:08.660
Even if Jingyuan and I

10:09.740 --> 10:10.990
are his pawns in power games,

10:14.740 --> 10:15.860
he loves us anyway.

11:07.740 --> 11:09.260
Now it is time.

11:26.830 --> 11:28.620
Marshal Duan is a military genius.

11:29.310 --> 11:30.470
Now, we've taken

11:30.470 --> 11:31.430
several cities

11:31.430 --> 11:32.270
around Youzhou.

11:33.540 --> 11:34.620
The last few battles...

11:35.260 --> 11:36.100
Really exhilarating.

11:38.470 --> 11:39.470
What are our casualties?

11:41.110 --> 11:42.500
Guihe Army lost 20 percent.

11:43.620 --> 11:45.140
Tabai Army and Chengjie Army lost

11:46.140 --> 11:47.110
nearly 30,000 soldiers.

11:52.660 --> 11:53.500
Bury them properly.

11:55.900 --> 11:56.740
The next battle

11:57.830 --> 11:58.950
will determine

11:58.950 --> 11:59.790
the outcome.

12:00.710 --> 12:02.180
(Youzhou)
Youzhou is the Chong's key.

12:02.540 --> 12:03.500
They'll defend fully.

12:03.900 --> 12:04.740
From tomorrow on,

12:06.070 --> 12:07.070
we'll fight for survival.

12:07.990 --> 12:09.280
We pledge our lives

12:09.660 --> 12:11.230
to the capture of Youzhou!

12:11.730 --> 12:13.260
- Capture!
- Capture Youzhou!

12:21.190 --> 12:22.030
Captain Han is here.

12:24.110 --> 12:25.540
Han.

12:35.590 --> 12:36.430
I...

12:38.500 --> 12:39.340
I'm late.

12:42.590 --> 12:43.430
Lingqiu.

12:47.110 --> 12:47.950
I shouldn't have left.

12:49.070 --> 12:49.910
If I had been here,

12:51.900 --> 12:52.740
Chenying wouldn't...

13:02.500 --> 13:03.710
If we get a complete victory...

13:04.110 --> 13:04.950
Tomorrow,

13:05.990 --> 13:06.860
we'll follow the plan.

13:08.500 --> 13:09.340
Yes.

13:12.310 --> 13:13.260
Han,

13:13.260 --> 13:14.230
I missed you so much.

13:41.590 --> 13:42.780
The elixir you made

13:43.140 --> 13:44.260
is remarkably effective.

13:44.950 --> 13:46.310
I spared no effort to nurse him

13:46.470 --> 13:47.430
and cast a blessed spell.

13:48.230 --> 13:49.230
But Duan Xu...

13:50.900 --> 13:52.020
He's been working all day

13:52.020 --> 13:52.860
and draining himself.

13:53.540 --> 13:54.380
I...

13:55.660 --> 13:56.990
I'll just do the best I can.

14:00.430 --> 14:01.270
How long has he got?

14:02.780 --> 14:04.260
If he takes good rest,

14:05.990 --> 14:06.950
perhaps,

14:08.350 --> 14:09.950
he can live as long as I can.

14:14.540 --> 14:16.020
If he could take good rest,

14:17.430 --> 14:18.500
he wouldn't be Duan Xu.

14:19.860 --> 14:21.430
If he keeps exhausting himself,

14:21.830 --> 14:23.310
even if he has my blessed spell

14:23.470 --> 14:24.470
and full recuperation,

14:24.780 --> 14:25.620
he...

14:28.430 --> 14:29.590
He has only two years left.

14:45.350 --> 14:47.710
♪I go alone in the night without end♪

14:47.740 --> 14:48.580
No.

14:50.430 --> 14:51.900
Foxy has

14:52.260 --> 14:53.380
a charmed life.

14:53.380 --> 14:55.990
♪Wishful thoughts creep onto my brows♪

14:56.430 --> 14:57.990
He'll always survive.

15:00.660 --> 15:03.970
♪Through cycles of time, we get to meet♪

15:04.550 --> 15:07.380
♪Snow on sunny days♪

15:07.920 --> 15:10.210
♪Countless wayfarers roam the world♪

15:10.400 --> 15:17.450
♪Luckily, I share a fate with you♪

15:19.550 --> 15:22.960
♪I hold a lantern to draw the moon♪

15:23.300 --> 15:27.320
♪Light up the night that haunts you♪

15:27.830 --> 15:31.770
♪I have simple wishes, but I fear♪

15:31.770 --> 15:34.810
♪The world can't hold them♪

15:35.000 --> 15:38.300
♪You always stay with me♪

15:38.780 --> 15:42.560
♪See the world I've never seen♪

15:43.240 --> 15:47.280
♪However the years may wind♪

15:47.280 --> 15:56.040
♪I wish I could live in your heart♪

16:41.900 --> 16:42.740
Simu,

16:43.660 --> 16:44.950
you think you can stop me

16:44.950 --> 16:46.140
by sealing off the passage

16:46.590 --> 16:48.350
between the Void and the Mortal World?

16:51.900 --> 16:53.470
I'll turn the Mortal World

16:53.740 --> 16:55.380
into my battlefield too.

16:58.380 --> 17:02.420
(Liang)

17:28.020 --> 17:29.060
Liang soldiers,

17:29.780 --> 17:30.710
in today's battle,

17:31.870 --> 17:32.910
we'll annihilate enemies

17:33.780 --> 17:34.990
and reclaim our land!

17:35.340 --> 17:38.260
Annihilate enemies! Reclaim our land!

17:38.630 --> 17:41.630
Annihilate enemies! Reclaim our land!

17:41.950 --> 17:44.950
Annihilate enemies! Reclaim our land!

17:45.430 --> 17:48.430
Annihilate enemies! Reclaim our land!

17:48.740 --> 17:51.740
Annihilate enemies! Reclaim our land!

17:52.190 --> 17:55.190
Annihilate enemies! Reclaim our land!

17:56.870 --> 17:58.580
Charge!

17:58.740 --> 18:05.430
Kill! Kill!

18:21.300 --> 18:25.500
Kill!

20:10.990 --> 20:11.830
Your Grace!

20:13.910 --> 20:14.750
Your Grace,

20:14.970 --> 20:15.820
bad news.

20:15.820 --> 20:16.730
On the battlefield,

20:16.730 --> 20:18.020
many spirit soldiers appeared.

20:18.510 --> 20:19.690
Liang troops couldn't resist

20:20.340 --> 20:21.580
and suffered heavy casualties.

20:22.190 --> 20:23.030
It's Yan Ke.

20:24.150 --> 20:25.150
He actually created

20:25.150 --> 20:26.670
so many spirit soldiers in this world

20:27.150 --> 20:28.540
and even sent them to war.

20:28.780 --> 20:29.620
Fengyi,

20:29.910 --> 20:30.820
you go with me.

21:33.710 --> 21:35.020
Liang soldiers,

21:37.230 --> 21:38.150
how are you?

21:40.870 --> 21:41.710
Are you all right?

21:44.230 --> 21:45.670
Puppet spirits are tough to kill.

21:46.870 --> 21:48.340
My sword can fight them.

21:49.430 --> 21:50.440
But there are too many.

21:51.260 --> 21:52.360
I can't kill them all.

21:56.780 --> 21:57.740
(I must do something)

21:57.740 --> 21:58.620
(to help Her Grace.)

22:02.740 --> 22:04.020
Oh, my eyes.

22:04.990 --> 22:05.830
Hold on there.

22:10.020 --> 22:11.670
(As long as I sense the Glazed Pagoda,)

22:12.190 --> 22:13.100
(I'll find Yan Ke.)

22:13.780 --> 22:15.020
(Then I can help Her Grace.)

22:42.110 --> 22:43.020
You said the spirits

22:43.020 --> 22:44.150
would only fight my enemies.

22:44.700 --> 22:46.410
Why are they fighting my troops too?

22:48.060 --> 22:49.230
Why do you care

22:49.230 --> 22:50.670
about such insignificant lives?

22:51.780 --> 22:52.910
Now on this battlefield,

22:52.910 --> 22:55.670
thousands of auras are mine to feast on.

22:58.670 --> 23:00.710
Defeating He Simu won't be a problem.

23:09.150 --> 23:11.260
When I become the Sovereign,

23:12.430 --> 23:14.190
I'll give you as many troops

23:14.580 --> 23:16.190
as you want.

23:16.820 --> 23:17.990
You shameless fiend!

23:18.390 --> 23:19.700
How dare you kill my people!

23:28.260 --> 23:29.110
Don't think

23:29.110 --> 23:30.820
you can rant before me

23:31.540 --> 23:33.350
just because you have
the Lantern's power.

23:43.630 --> 23:45.020
This method of cultivation...

23:46.230 --> 23:47.670
I'll teach you only once.

23:48.990 --> 23:50.340
Keep it in mind.

23:54.230 --> 23:55.390
You're nothing but a puppet

23:55.390 --> 23:57.430
I've made.

24:05.430 --> 24:06.670
From now on,

24:07.430 --> 24:10.430
the Spirits Lantern will serve me.

24:25.150 --> 24:26.160
Glazed Pagoda?

24:48.340 --> 24:49.990
You want to dissolve me?

24:50.910 --> 24:52.670
But the Lantern won't allow it!

25:43.300 --> 25:44.140
Yan Ke,

25:44.740 --> 25:46.060
I'm going to take you on.

26:02.780 --> 26:03.670
Your Grace.

26:03.670 --> 26:04.510
Simu?

26:04.740 --> 26:05.580
There you are.

26:05.800 --> 26:07.490
Leave now or die.

26:08.710 --> 26:09.550
Yes.

26:10.870 --> 26:12.150
Traitor Yan Ke,

26:13.150 --> 26:14.240
as the Right Hand,

26:14.660 --> 26:15.700
you violated the Decrees,

26:15.900 --> 26:17.460
disrupted the Void,
and plagued the Mortal World.

26:18.100 --> 26:19.580
I'll take you back to the Void

26:19.580 --> 26:20.420
and execute you.

26:27.060 --> 26:28.220
Then give it a try.

26:40.000 --> 26:40.880
Kill me here

26:41.260 --> 26:42.700
or go save those mortals.

26:42.940 --> 26:43.940
Make your choice.

26:44.340 --> 26:45.560
Even now,

26:46.860 --> 26:47.920
you're still playing

26:47.920 --> 26:48.900
such a dirty trick.

26:49.780 --> 26:50.660
You keep saying

26:50.660 --> 26:51.780
you want to be the Sovereign.

26:52.500 --> 26:53.730
But you hide all the time

26:53.740 --> 26:55.220
and don't even dare

26:55.220 --> 26:56.060
to fight me head-on.

26:56.680 --> 26:57.900
Even Bai Sanxing surpasses you.

26:58.580 --> 26:59.560
In my eyes,

26:59.900 --> 27:01.660
you're just a mere rebel.

27:02.650 --> 27:04.480
Today, I'll give you a chance.

27:04.890 --> 27:05.900
Kill me

27:06.910 --> 27:08.000
and you'll be the Sovereign.

27:09.740 --> 27:11.080
Am I that despicable

27:11.660 --> 27:13.630
in your eyes?

27:31.020 --> 27:31.860
Stay where you are.

28:39.060 --> 28:40.100
They won't disappear

28:41.020 --> 28:42.100
until Great Ancestor

28:42.660 --> 28:43.620
defeats Yan Ke

28:45.220 --> 28:46.740
at the source.

29:34.620 --> 29:35.460
They're killable now.

29:35.820 --> 29:36.660
They're dead.

29:47.540 --> 29:48.380
It's...

29:49.180 --> 29:50.260
Liang soldiers,

29:51.340 --> 29:52.860
I've refined your weapons.

29:53.540 --> 29:54.660
Now you can also kill

29:54.660 --> 29:55.500
these puppet spirits.

30:01.250 --> 30:02.100
Prophet,

30:02.200 --> 30:03.630
you should have used

30:03.940 --> 30:05.980
this awesome technique long ago!

30:44.100 --> 30:44.940
Soldiers!

30:46.060 --> 30:48.060
Let's fight for our nation!

30:48.500 --> 30:51.340
Kill!

31:35.340 --> 31:36.180
Yan Ke,

31:37.300 --> 31:38.740
you lost after all.

31:40.060 --> 31:40.900
No.

31:42.220 --> 31:43.420
I never lost.

31:45.660 --> 31:46.900
In the past 300 years,

31:47.780 --> 31:48.980
your trust,

31:50.900 --> 31:51.740
reliance,

31:53.260 --> 31:54.100
and closeness to me

31:55.340 --> 31:56.580
were all fake.

31:57.500 --> 31:58.340
He Simu,

31:59.180 --> 32:00.820
you failed me!

32:03.220 --> 32:04.940
Your arrogant father

32:06.260 --> 32:07.980
treated me as a pawn.

32:10.020 --> 32:12.980
He used me and abandoned me.

32:13.620 --> 32:14.700
So did you.

32:20.140 --> 32:23.140
Those I adored all failed me.

32:24.180 --> 32:25.540
So I had to hold power

32:25.540 --> 32:26.820
in my own hands.

32:28.020 --> 32:29.340
What you didn't want to give me,

32:31.500 --> 32:33.380
I would grab it myself.

32:34.580 --> 32:37.450
All this should have been mine!

32:40.500 --> 32:42.340
All you have is selfish desire.

32:43.060 --> 32:44.540
All you strive for is vanity.

32:45.580 --> 32:47.460
I gave you the power you wanted.

32:47.780 --> 32:49.280
But your insatiable greed

32:49.280 --> 32:50.210
was hard to satisfy.

32:50.380 --> 32:51.230
That's why you thought

32:51.230 --> 32:52.380
everyone failed you.

32:53.320 --> 32:54.360
As for the Lantern...

32:54.780 --> 32:55.730
In your eyes,

32:55.730 --> 32:56.960
it's a supreme treasure.

32:57.580 --> 32:58.520
But to me,

32:58.520 --> 32:59.960
it's just like the throne.

33:01.300 --> 33:02.140
A mere object.

33:31.460 --> 33:33.570
Just because of evil spirits like you,

33:33.980 --> 33:35.820
my father and my siblings

33:36.420 --> 33:37.820
lost their lives!

33:38.860 --> 33:39.700
Let go.

33:40.180 --> 33:41.580
You can't control the Lantern.

33:53.860 --> 33:55.300
You're the Sovereign.

33:56.980 --> 33:58.700
If you vanish,

33:59.620 --> 34:00.460
perhaps then,

34:01.860 --> 34:03.180
all the evil spirits in this world

34:03.180 --> 34:04.460
will disappear!

34:08.620 --> 34:09.460
No!

34:11.550 --> 34:12.570
Stop!

34:22.100 --> 34:22.940
Simu.

35:02.540 --> 35:03.380
No.

35:04.260 --> 35:05.100
Simu.

35:17.060 --> 35:17.900
(I...)

35:19.660 --> 35:20.900
(I can finally die.)

35:24.060 --> 35:24.900
(It's not bad.)

35:26.700 --> 35:28.300
(I no longer have to endure loneliness)

35:29.260 --> 35:30.100
(or bear the pain)

35:30.100 --> 35:31.820
(of being left behind by those I love.)

35:34.740 --> 35:35.580
(Father.)

35:37.540 --> 35:38.380
(Mother.)

35:40.020 --> 35:41.180
(I'm coming to you.)

36:23.700 --> 36:24.540
The Void is quaking.

36:25.020 --> 36:25.860
He Simu's in trouble.

36:27.660 --> 36:28.500
Let's secure this.

36:28.780 --> 36:29.970
Spirits can't enter the Mortal World.

36:42.190 --> 36:45.360
♪Falling down like snow♪

36:45.380 --> 36:46.300
Simu is in trouble.

36:46.370 --> 36:49.850
♪Joys and sorrows of the mortal world♪

36:49.850 --> 36:53.730
♪Swept along by the daylight♪

36:54.140 --> 36:57.940
♪The forms and hues of the mortal realm♪

36:58.210 --> 37:00.880
♪Lingering for a fleeting moment♪

37:01.040 --> 37:05.360
♪Was once touched by laughing tears♪

37:05.840 --> 37:08.750
♪If I could live a simple life♪

37:08.750 --> 37:09.590
♪For once♪

37:09.590 --> 37:11.840
♪I'd be a guest in a sweet dream♪

37:11.860 --> 37:13.820
That's He Simu's vital gate, isn't it?

37:16.760 --> 37:20.260
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

37:20.440 --> 37:24.060
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

37:24.570 --> 37:28.180
♪Let me wander through♪

37:28.180 --> 37:31.820
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

37:32.230 --> 37:35.630
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

37:35.760 --> 37:39.760
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

37:39.970 --> 37:42.660
♪As all things turn and flow♪

37:42.780 --> 37:48.690
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

38:02.780 --> 38:06.330
♪As stars shift and change places♪

38:06.580 --> 38:10.270
♪A century is like a dream♪

38:10.460 --> 38:14.040
♪Let me journey across them all♪

38:14.240 --> 38:17.730
♪Without reincarnations♪

38:19.780 --> 38:20.660
You little ant.

38:21.500 --> 38:22.780
How dare you?

38:25.840 --> 38:28.920
♪Moments may last♪

38:28.920 --> 38:33.600
♪Love and hate will fade away♪

38:33.620 --> 38:36.620
Leave! Leave!

38:40.420 --> 38:41.260
Xu.

38:43.740 --> 38:44.580
Simu is in trouble.

38:45.020 --> 38:45.860
According to Prophet,

38:46.140 --> 38:47.780
these spirit soldiers won't disappear

38:47.780 --> 38:49.260
until Yan Ke is defeated!

38:49.500 --> 38:50.860
Nothing shall happen to Miss He!

38:52.940 --> 38:54.660
Xu, we can't kill

38:54.660 --> 38:56.100
all these spirit soldiers on our own.

38:56.420 --> 38:57.440
We'll take care of them.

38:57.700 --> 38:58.970
You go help Miss He.

38:59.380 --> 39:00.220
Go!

39:11.180 --> 39:12.020
You must stay alive!

39:12.150 --> 39:13.860
Yes!

39:13.860 --> 39:14.700
- Yes!
- Yes!

39:15.660 --> 39:16.580
Maizi,

39:16.580 --> 39:17.420
take me to Simu.

39:18.740 --> 39:19.580
All right.

39:44.020 --> 39:44.860
(I'm all alone,)

39:45.420 --> 39:47.540
(eternal and undying.)

40:08.660 --> 40:09.500
(How nice.)

40:10.540 --> 40:11.940
(I'm no longer lonely.)

40:52.240 --> 40:57.570
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:57.900 --> 41:02.150
♪Light encountered shadow♪

41:03.510 --> 41:08.880
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

41:09.180 --> 41:13.780
♪The unbreakable fate♪

41:14.870 --> 41:16.710
♪Suddenly cracked♪

41:28.920 --> 41:34.360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

41:34.540 --> 41:38.870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

41:40.240 --> 41:45.630
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

41:45.860 --> 41:49.800
♪The unbreakable fate♪

41:51.570 --> 41:53.460
♪Suddenly cracked♪

41:56.120 --> 41:59.280
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

41:59.280 --> 42:01.810
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

42:01.810 --> 42:07.330
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

42:07.330 --> 42:10.570
♪Following fate's guidance♪

42:10.570 --> 42:15.430
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

42:15.770 --> 42:18.790
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

42:18.790 --> 42:21.610
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

42:21.870 --> 42:24.400
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

42:24.400 --> 42:29.820
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

42:29.990 --> 42:33.060
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

42:33.220 --> 42:38.120
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

42:38.330 --> 42:41.800
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
